- int left = 0, right = 0;
  int windowSum = 0;

  while (right < n) {
      windowSum += arr[right];

      if (right - left + 1 == k) {
          // answer update
          windowSum -= arr[left];
          left++;
      }
      right++;
  }

- Max sum subarray of size k
- Average of subarrays of size k
- First negative number in every window of size k

